IA-642 Lab 4: Wazuh Manager & Agent Lab

Overview:
Lab for installing Wazuh Manager and Agents, simulating attacks, and viewing alerts.

Files:
Wazuh-Manger-Ubuntu.sh - Installs Wazuh Manager
Wazuh-Agent-Ubuntu.sh - Installs Wazuh Agent on Ubuntu
Wazuh-Agent-Windows.ps1 - Installs Wazuh Agent on Windows
Kali-Attack-Simulation.sh - Simulates failed logins, sudo abuse, and scans

Usage:
Install Wazuh Manager:
sudo bash Wazuh-Manger-Ubuntu.sh

Install Ubuntu Agent:
sudo bash Wazuh-Agent-Ubuntu.sh

Install Windows Agent:
.\Wazuh-Agent-Windows.ps1

Run attack simulation:
bash Kali-Attack-Simulation.sh